&lt;img src="https://r2.337845818.best/oss-to-r2/2024/07/07/668a455faaf9e.png"
loading="lazy"
alt="Proxy Checker"
>
测试无误后，我们进入这个&lt;code>Proxification Rules&lt;/code>配置代理规则：
&lt;div class="post-img-view">
&lt;a data-fancybox="gallery" href="https://r2.337845818.best/oss-to-r2/2024/07/07/668a45aa5a338.png">
